::Magmatron::

    Waking from a brief nap he sees the Destrocons just out side of the base, 
they are calling to be let in.  
    "Autoguns stand down," Magmatron said as they took aim. They now hang 
limp. "Outer doors open, close all inner door except ones leading directly to 
my Conference room."
    The outer doors opened and all the doors that didn't go from the outside 
to the Conference room were shut and locked. This means that everybody in 
stuck where they are for now. He went to the Conference room, the doors would 
open for him, but only him. He sat down and waited for the Destrocons to 
enter and find their way to the Conference room, it shouldn't be that hard.


(OOC: Yanshosh I've been wondering why my base isn't put up on the events 
board. Is it that you don't know where it is? It's in India. Which is still 
mostly island at this point, if we are 4 million years ago, or is it more?)
